<br>
Oh, and by the way, druids all over will attack you if you are fighting a wolf or bear, including commonlands.  Doesn't matter who started it.  Also, I've hunted rabid animals in QH and have never had a problem with Holly, you just need to glance around you every once in a while to make sure you're alone. <p>Brion (Raydon) <BR>
